{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a shooting game where you blow away a futon with a rocket launcher.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player set out on a journey with his partner Rocket Launcher to clean the Futon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The goal is a cleaning spot 1km away. No matter what, don't drop the futon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*&quot;Futon ga Futtonda&quot;,&quot;Blow up the Futon&quot; is a famous Japanese pun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game rules</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1.Shoot the futon with the rocket launcher and it will fly away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2.If you shoot the futon in the air, you can make it fly even further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3.Repeat this to make the futon fly farther.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4.If you drop the futon on the ground, the game is over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game consists of multiple levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a story mode where you aim for the futon cleaning spot 1km away, and a challenge mode where you aim to fly the futon farther.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have to pick up the rocket launcher ammo that is falling on the ground as you move along.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies that appear along the way will attack the futon and try to make it fall to the ground, so use the rocket launcher to fight them off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can enjoy a moderate amount of thrill as you have to fight and collect ammunition while being careful not to drop the futon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rankings will be released after clearing the game. You can compete with players from all over the world to see how far the futon flies.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Level1 Clear","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3297010/ead13a2eb865ba1063f7d3513b94b6572105c407.jpg"},{"name":